            "creation_date": 1466944839,
            "body": "<p>You are doing the Update on a Thread with Background Priority....<\/p>\n\n<p>You will have to do run it on main Thread<\/p>\n\n<p>Change this line:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>holderProfile.setImageBitmap(image);\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>To this:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>runOnUiThread(new Runnable() {\n      @Override public void run() {\n            holderProfile.setImageBitmap(image);\n      }\n});\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
            "answer_id": 38038593,
            "question_id": 38038574,
            "last_edit_date": 1466945212
        },
